We accompany you at every step of your project towards self-consumption

   Simulation
   Validation
   Installation
   Control & Warranty
   Production & Savings
   Simulation

   Comwatt presents me with a personalized project for self-consumption,
   adapted to my situation, for free and without any commitment.
   Validation

   We connect you directly with one of our 300 certified technicians, who
   visit you at home in order to examine your project with you and make
   you an offer for a personalized plan, as well as help you with the
   funding.
   Installation

   The installation is completed by your assigned photovoltaic installer,
   who is trained and selected according to our demanding quality
   standards.
   Control & Warranty

   Comwatt controls remotely the quality of my solar energy set-up, and my
   Comwatt equipment has a 15-year warranty.
   Production & Savings

   You are now self-producing your energy. This option allows you to save
   money and to keep track in real time of your energy self-sufficiency.
